snippet.title: FENIX Interview: Meet Acclaimed Artist & Producer AMBER WILSON!
snippet.description:
Join The Change. FENIX’s revolutionary blockchain platform is designed to better connect artists and fans in a way where everybody benefits. Designed to give artists multiple new income sources, FENIX provides them with direct access to the music merchandise and ticketing industries - in a way that’s never been done before. For more, please visit https://www.fenix360.net 

For more on AMBER WILSON:
Instagram: https://instagram.com/musicfromamber?utm_medium=copy_link
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/musicfromamber/
Youtube: https://youtube.com/c/amberwilson
TikTok: https://vm.tiktok.com/ZM8LrVvGW/
SoundCloud: https://soundcloud.app.goo.gl/gpx9wzUKEtqsPP9P6
Bandcamp: https://amberwilson.bandcamp.com
